headline: CoStar Group To Present at Stephens 27th Annual Investment Conference
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., November 17, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, will present at Stephens 27th Annual Investment Conference. CFO Chris Lown and Head of Investor Relations Rich Simonelli will participate in a fireside chat on Thursday, November 20, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. CT. headline: How Zillow makes money
summary: Zillow is the most widely used real estate app in the United States. The Seattle-based tech firm provides property price estimates and other data previously available only to Realtors in the MLS system. Today, many real estate agents rely on Zillow to generate leads that produce commissions. The company’s stock has underperformed the broader market as it wades through a series of legal challenges.
